  "description": "Fix Gallery Card Image Aspect Ratio to Allow Counter Overlay\n\nRemove the fixed 4/3 aspect ratio constraint from gallery card images to enable proper visual overlay of the counter element.\n\nRequirements:\n- Locate the gallery-card-image component or CSS class definition\n- Remove or modify the aspect-ratio: 4/3 property\n- Ensure images display at their natural aspect ratio or use a more flexible sizing approach\n- Verify the counter element now properly overlays the image without layout issues\n- Test with images of various aspect ratios (portrait, landscape, square) to ensure counter positioning remains consistent\n- Confirm no unintended layout shifts or breaking changes in the gallery grid",
